                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="64" value="&lt;h3&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Courier New&quot;&gt;Linking files&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;" style="swimlane;fontStyle=0;childLayout=stackLayout;horizontal=1;startSize=30;horizontalStack=0;resizeParent=1;resizeParentMax=0;resizeLast=0;collapsible=1;marginBottom=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=1;fillColor=#b1ddf0;strokeColor=#10739e;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="460" y="1400" width="300" height="90" as="geometry">
                        <mxRectangle x="440" y="1400" width="150" height="60" as="alternateBounds"/>
                    </mxGeometry>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="65" value="1.&amp;nbsp; Hard Links and Symlinks(Symbolic links): - The diff is &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(0, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;Hard links points to data in the disk&lt;/font&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; while &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(255, 51, 153));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;symlink point to the file&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;" style="text;strokeColor=default;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;rotatable=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;dashed=1;dashPattern=1 4;" parent="64" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry y="30" width="300" height="60" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="68" value="&lt;h3&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Courier New&quot;&gt;Hard Link&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;" style="swimlane;fontStyle=0;childLayout=stackLayout;horizontal=1;startSize=30;horizontalStack=0;resizeParent=1;resizeParentMax=0;resizeLast=0;collapsible=1;marginBottom=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=1;fillColor=#b1ddf0;strokeColor=#10739e;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="250" y="1590" width="300" height="80" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="69" value="1. reating a new directory entry that points to the exact same physical data (the same &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;170&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;inode&lt;/b&gt;) on your storage drive&amp;nbsp;" style="text;strokeColor=default;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;rotatable=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;dashed=1;dashPattern=1 4;" vertex="1" parent="68">
                    <mxGeometry y="30" width="300" height="50" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="70" value="&lt;h3&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Courier New&quot;&gt;Soft link&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;" style="swimlane;fontStyle=0;childLayout=stackLayout;horizontal=1;startSize=30;horizontalStack=0;resizeParent=1;resizeParentMax=0;resizeLast=0;collapsible=1;marginBottom=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=1;fillColor=#b1ddf0;strokeColor=#10739e;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="690" y="1600" width="300" height="90" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="71" value="1. A symbolic link acts like a &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;28&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;shortcut&lt;/b&gt; or a pointer. While a hard link points to the actual data on the disk, a symbolic link points to the &lt;b data-index-in-node=&quot;138&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;file path&lt;/b&gt; of the target file" style="text;strokeColor=default;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;rotatable=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;dashed=1;dashPattern=1 4;" vertex="1" parent="70">
                    <mxGeometry y="30" width="300" height="60" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="66" value="&lt;h3&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot; face=&quot;Courier New&quot;&gt;Practicals to do for file system&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;" style="swimlane;fontStyle=0;childLayout=stackLayout;horizontal=1;startSize=30;horizontalStack=0;resizeParent=1;resizeParentMax=0;resizeLast=0;collapsible=1;marginBottom=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=1;fillColor=light-dark(#D80073,#E51400);strokeColor=#A50040;fontColor=#ffffff;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1130" y="1340" width="310" height="150" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="67" value="1. Create a &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(0, 102, 204));&quot;&gt;Hard link&lt;/span&gt; for any file, and make changes in any of the linked files and then notices the changes in all the linked files" style="text;strokeColor=default;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;rotatable=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;dashed=1;dashPattern=1 4;" vertex="1" parent="66">
                    <mxGeometry y="30" width="310" height="60" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="74" value="2. Create a &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(0, 102, 204));&quot;&gt;Soft link&lt;/span&gt; for any file, and make changes in that soft linked files and then notices the changes in the actual file" style="text;strokeColor=default;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;rotatable=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;dashed=1;dashPattern=1 4;" vertex="1" parent="66">
                    <mxGeometry y="90" width="310" height="60" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
